---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { getLangFromUrl, useTranslations, useTranslatedPath } from '../i18n/utils';
import { Sparkles, BookOpen, Anchor, Map, Ship } from 'lucide-astro';

const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const t = useTranslations(lang);
const translatePath = useTranslatedPath(lang);

const title = lang === 'zh' ? '七年的故事' : 'A Seven-Year Story';
const description = lang === 'zh'
  ? '莫拉船长、莫里和辛塔, 在龟岛上过了七年。'
  : 'Captain Mora, Mori, and Cinta. Seven years on Turtle Island.';

const years = [
  {
    id: 'y1',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? '第一年「启航」' : 'Year 1 "Setting Out"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '你不是一个人出发的' : 'You\'re not setting off alone',
    image: '/v2/chapters/chapter_y1_prologue.webp',
    color: 'tide-gold',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '"光, 是这样从一个人, 传到另一个人的。"'
      : '"Light, this is how it passes from one to the next."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '出发那天, 莫拉船长慢慢走进了海里。这是他那一年唯一一次下水, 也是莫里第一次出门。那一年, 莫里点亮了三十颗小小的光。'
      : 'The day they set out, Captain Mora walked slowly into the sea. It was his only time in the water that year, and Mori\'s first journey out. That year, Mori lit thirty small lights.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y2',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? '第二年「远潮」' : 'Year 2 "Distant Tides"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '走过岛边的雾' : 'Walking past the mist',
    image: '/v2/chapters/chapter_y2_prologue.webp',
    color: 'deep-cyan',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '"那边, 你能走多远, 就走多远。"'
      : '"Out there — go as far as you can."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '岛边外面一直有一圈白色的雾。那一年, 莫里走进了雾里。他在很远的地方, 看见一只年轻的小海龟在往前走 — 看了一会, 才认出那是年轻时候的莫拉船长。'
      : 'Beyond the island there\'s always been a ring of white mist. That year, Mori walked into it. Far ahead, he saw a young turtle walking forward — only after a while did he realize it was Captain Mora, when Captain was young.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y3',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? '第三年「回响」' : 'Year 3 "The Echo"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '今天自己出发' : 'Going on his own today',
    image: '/v2/chapters/chapter_y3_prologue.webp',
    color: 'tide-gold',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '"你自己都知道。"'
      : '"You already know yourself."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '岛上最高处的龟脊树, 长出了第一片叶子。那天早上, 莫里看了一眼船长, 决定今天自己出发。'
      : 'On the highest point of the island, the Spineback Tree grew its first leaf. That morning, Mori glanced at Captain Mora, then set out on his own.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y4',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? '第四年「沉钟」' : 'Year 4 "The Sunken Bell"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '比船长更深的地方' : 'Deeper than Captain ever went',
    image: '/v2/chapters/chapter_y4_prologue.webp',
    color: 'deep-cyan',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '"你去了比我更深的地方。"'
      : '"You\'ve gone to a place deeper than I have."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '那一年, 莫里下潜到一个连船长都没去过的深处。最深的地方, 有一口很大的钟。他轻轻碰了一下, 钟没响, 但海面上的鱼都听见了。'
      : 'That year, Mori dove to a place even Captain hadn\'t been. At the deepest point, a great bell. He touched it lightly. The bell didn\'t ring, but every fish on the surface heard it.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y5',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? '第五年「古龟族」' : 'Year 5 "The Ancient Kin"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '你也在这个故事里' : 'You\'re in this story too',
    image: '/v2/chapters/chapter_y5_prologue.webp',
    color: 'tide-gold',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '"你是一段很长的故事的一部分。"'
      : '"You are part of a very long story."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '那一年, 莫拉船长说: "今年我不下水了, 你自己走。" 莫里在海里看见七个影子, 像很老很老的小海龟。他们看了莫里一眼, 然后慢慢淡了。'
      : 'That year, Captain Mora said: "I\'m not getting in the water this year. You go on your own." Mori saw seven shapes in the sea — like very, very old young turtles. They looked at him, then slowly faded.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y6',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? '第六年「守岛」' : 'Year 6 "Guardian"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '现在轮到你照顾别人' : 'Now it\'s your turn to look after someone',
    image: '/v2/scenes/mori_at_island.webp',
    color: 'deep-cyan',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '"他抓着一块漂木。莫里认得那块。"'
      : '"He was holding a piece of driftwood. Mori knew that one."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '那年浅水里漂来了一只小海龟, 抓着一块漂木。莫里认得那块漂木 — 是他几年前推回大海的。小海龟有点怕。莫里看着她, 跟船长当年看莫里的眼神, 一样。她叫辛塔。'
      : 'That year, a small turtle washed up in the shallows, holding a piece of driftwood. Mori knew that piece — he\'d pushed it back into the sea a few years before. She was a bit scared. Mori looked at her the way Captain Mora had once looked at him. Her name is Cinta.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y7',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? '第七年「黎明」' : 'Year 7 "Dawn"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '灯塔交给你了' : 'The lighthouse is yours now',
    image: '/v2/scenes/mori_lighthouse.webp',
    color: 'tide-gold',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '"灯塔交给你了。"'
      : '"The lighthouse is yours now."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '那天早上, 雾, 没了。海, 蓝, 一直蓝到看不见。莫拉船长留了一封很短的信, 然后走了。莫里在那个早上点亮了灯塔, 灯光照向辛塔的方向。'
      : 'That morning, the mist was gone. The sea was blue, all the way out. Captain Mora left a very short note, then walked. Mori lit the lighthouse that morning, and the lamp shone toward Cinta.'
  }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-24 space-y-6">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 glass rounded-full text-xs font-black text-brand-blue uppercase tracking-widest animate-fade-in">
           <Sparkles size={14} /> <span>{lang === 'zh' ? '七年' : 'SEVEN YEARS'}</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black dark:text-slate-300 tracking-tight">
          {lang === 'zh' ? '莫里的' : 'Mori\'s'} <span class="text-gradient">{lang === 'zh' ? '七年' : 'Seven Years'}</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed">
          {lang === 'zh'
            ? '一年一段。莫拉船长一直在岛上, 莫里在海里慢慢长大, 第六年遇到辛塔。'
            : 'One chapter per year. Captain Mora stays on the island. Mori grows up in the sea. In Year 6, he meets Cinta.'}
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline -->
      <div class="relative space-y-32">
        <!-- Center Line (Desktop) -->
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-blue/20 via-brand-green/20 to-transparent -translate-x-1/2 hidden md:block"></div>

        {years.map((year, index) => (
          <div class={`relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 ${index % 2 === 1 ? 'md:flex-row-reverse' : ''}`}>
            <!-- Image Card -->
            <div class="flex-1 w-full group">
              <div class="glass-frame p-2 organic-radius overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transition-all duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.02] group-hover:-rotate-1">
                <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden organic-radius">
                  <img src={year.image} alt={year.title} class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-110" />
                  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity flex flex-col justify-end p-8">
                     <p class="text-white font-bold italic text-lg leading-relaxed">{year.quote}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Indicator Dot -->
            <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-12 h-12 glass rounded-full hidden md:flex items-center justify-center z-10 shadow-xl border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-900">
               <div class={`w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-${year.color} animate-pulse`}></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Content Card -->
            <div class="flex-1 space-y-6 text-center md:text-left">
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <span class={`text-sm font-black text-${year.color} uppercase tracking-widest`}>{year.title}</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black dark:text-slate-300">{year.subtitle}</h2>
              </div>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                {year.content}
              </p>

              <div class="pt-4 flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start gap-4">
                <div class="px-4 py-2 glass rounded-xl flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                   {index === 0 ? <Anchor size={16} /> : index === 3 ? <Ship size={16} /> : <Map size={16} />}
                   <span>{index === 0 ? 'Departure' : index === 3 ? 'Deep Dive' : 'Exploration'}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Final CTA -->
      <div class="mt-48 text-center glass rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-24 relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-green/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-1000"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 space-y-10">
           <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black dark:text-slate-300 leading-tight">
             {lang === 'zh' ? '莫里' : 'Mori is'} <br /><span class="text-gradient">{lang === 'zh' ? '在等你' : 'waiting'}</span>
           </h2>
           <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-xl mx-auto font-medium">
             {lang === 'zh'
               ? '七年才刚开始。'
               : 'Seven years is only just beginning.'}
           </p>
           <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-6">
              <a href={translatePath('/') + '#download'} class="px-10 py-5 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-3xl font-black text-lg shadow-2xl shadow-brand-blue/20 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all">
                {lang === 'zh' ? '下载 Tortoise' : 'Get Tortoise'}
              </a>
              <a href={translatePath('/gallery')} class="px-10 py-5 glass rounded-3xl font-black text-lg hover:bg-white/60 dark:hover:bg-gray-800/60 transition-all">
                {lang === 'zh' ? '看看图鉴' : 'See the Gallery'}
              </a>
           </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Decorative Background Image -->
        <img src="/v2/scenes/mori_lighthouse.webp" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-1000 pointer-events-none" alt="" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
